Odyssey'' in the Depression-era South. With George Clooney, John
Turturro, John Goodman, Holly Hunter.
</P>
<P>
   PROOF OF LIFE: Russell Crowe is a negotiator hired by a woman
(Meg Ryan) to free her abducted husband (David Morse) from Latin
American rebels.
</P>
