wants campaign finance reform - Rick Lazio,'' the Arizona senator
says.
</P>
<P>
   The president's letter ''about the Senate candidate I know
best'' warns that his wife's opponents ''will spare no expense and
respect no boundaries in their efforts to defeat her.''
</P>
<P>
   The president says he is making the appeal ''not just out of
personal interest, but also in the hope of advancing the values and
highest ideals of our party and our nation.''
